import React from 'react';
import { createMuiTheme, makeStyles, ThemeProvider } from '@material-ui/core/styles';
import Timeline from '@material-ui/lab/Timeline';
import TimelineItem from '@material-ui/lab/TimelineItem';
import TimelineSeparator from '@material-ui/lab/TimelineSeparator';
import TimelineConnector from '@material-ui/lab/TimelineConnector';
import TimelineContent from '@material-ui/lab/TimelineContent';
import TimelineOppositeContent from '@material-ui/lab/TimelineOppositeContent';
import TimelineDot from '@material-ui/lab/TimelineDot';
import Paper from '@material-ui/core/Paper';
import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography';

const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
    paper: {
        padding: '6px 16px',
    },
    secondaryTail: {
        backgroundColor: theme.palette.secondary.main,
    },

}));

export default function CustomizedTimeline() {
    const theme = React.useMemo(
        () =>
            createMuiTheme({
                palette: {
                    type: 'dark',
                },
            }),
        []
    );

    const classes = useStyles();

    return (
        <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
            <Timeline align="alternate">
                <TimelineItem>
                    <TimelineOppositeContent>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                        24th Januray 2023
                        </Typography>
                    </TimelineOppositeContent>
                    <TimelineSeparator>
                        <TimelineDot />
                        <TimelineConnector />
                    </TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineContent>
                        <Paper elevation={3} className={classes.paper}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" component="h1">
                                Registrations Start
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>You can register for our hackathon using the DevFolio link provided above.</Typography>
                        </Paper>
                    </TimelineContent>
                </TimelineItem>
                <TimelineItem>
                    <TimelineOppositeContent>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                        28th Jan 2022 - 5th Feb 2023
                        </Typography>
                    </TimelineOppositeContent>
                    <TimelineSeparator>
                        <TimelineDot />
                        <TimelineConnector />
                    </TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineContent>
                        <Paper elevation={3} className={classes.paper}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" component="h1">
                            Team Confirmation and RSVP
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>We will be reviewing and contacting the participants and confirming their participation.</Typography>
                        </Paper>
                    </TimelineContent>
                </TimelineItem>
                <TimelineItem>
                    <TimelineOppositeContent>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                        5th February 2022
                        </Typography>
                    </TimelineOppositeContent>
                    <TimelineSeparator>
                        <TimelineDot />
                        <TimelineConnector />
                    </TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineContent>
                        <Paper elevation={3} className={classes.paper}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" component="h1">
                            Registration End
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>We will be closing registrations and will be reviewing all remaining applicants.</Typography>
                        </Paper>
                    </TimelineContent>
                </TimelineItem>
                <TimelineItem>
                    <TimelineOppositeContent>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                        21st January 2022
                        </Typography>
                    </TimelineOppositeContent>
                    <TimelineSeparator>
                        <TimelineDot />
                        <TimelineConnector />
                    </TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineContent>
                        <Paper elevation={3} className={classes.paper}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" component="h1">
                            Release of Problem Statements
                            </Typography>
                        </Paper>
                    </TimelineContent>
                </TimelineItem>
                <TimelineItem>
                    <TimelineOppositeContent>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                        22nd January 2022
                        </Typography>
                    </TimelineOppositeContent>
                    <TimelineSeparator>
                        <TimelineDot />
                        <TimelineConnector />
                    </TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineContent>
                        <Paper elevation={3} className={classes.paper}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" component="h1">
                            Hackathon Begins
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>Let the HACKATHON begin..!!!</Typography>
                        </Paper>
                    </TimelineContent>
                </TimelineItem>
                <TimelineItem>
                    <TimelineOppositeContent>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
                        23rd January 2022
                        </Typography>
                    </TimelineOppositeContent>
                    <TimelineSeparator>
                        <TimelineDot />
                        <TimelineConnector />
                    </TimelineSeparator>
                    <TimelineContent>
                        <Paper elevation={3} className={classes.paper}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" component="h1">
                            Hackathon Ends
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography>The hackathon would end and we would contact winning teams for further processes.</Typography>
                        </Paper>
                    </TimelineContent>
                </TimelineItem>
            </Timeline>
        </ThemeProvider>
    );
}
